DESCRIPTION:Event Types: Arts\,Training-Classes/Workshops\n\nNeighborhoo ds
	: Citywide\,Online Event\n\nContact: smART Ventures Team\n\nContact Email:
	 smartventures@seattle.gov\n\nAudience: All\n\nPre-Register: Yes\n\nCost: 
	Free\n\nLink: https://www.seattle.gov/arts/programs/grants/smart-ventures-
	grant\n\nAfter reviewing the smART Ventures guidelines\, attend a group se
	ssion to learn how to submit your best application.\n\nSessions are availa
