	energy at the Third Annual 4/20 Live Showcase right in the south end of Se
	attle  ✨ Experience “Stardust”✨  Theme: Harlem Nights: 1920s–30s Edition ✨
	 Step into the glamour of a golden era. Dress in your best Harlem Nights a
	ttire — flapper dresses\, sharp pinstripes\, fedoras\, pearls\, suspenders
	\, and polished shoes. Bring the elegance. Bring the confidence. Bring the
	 vibe. This isn’t just a concert — it’s an experience. A space where magic
	 comes alive\, soulful sounds fill the room\, and culture meets class.\n\n
